longBusinessSummary: Qatar Cinema and Film Distribution Co. (Q.P.S.C) engages in the distribution of cinema films and videos in Qatar. It also trades in television films and programs, and tools for the operation of cinema and projectors. The company offers commercial advertisement services; and operates movie theaters, as well as cafeterias for cinemas. In addition, it invests in shares, bonds, funds, and real estate properties. Qatar Cinema and Film Distribution Co. (Q.P.S.C) was incorporated in 1970 and is based in Doha, Qatar.
